metadata.name: Amnesia
metadata.description:
I remember when I saw him we were friends first and I cant forget the time that we told each other we love each other. but this is not that night this is the night every thing was dark inside and outside of my heart the night we broke up I remember every detail of it I remember I saw everything red that night.  
yeah memories are not all good you know what maybe Amnesia is not that bad...

( a memory from Parmida ( the model of this photo).


Winter 2023

4000x6000 px
